        4707
      ],
      "content": "When using the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Azure preview portal<ept id=\"p1\">][preview-portal]</ept> to create a Linux-based HDInsight cluster, you must enter an <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>SSH Username<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, and select to enter a <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>PASSWORD<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> or <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>SSH PUBLIC KEY<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>."
