        7520
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Connect to worker nodes",
      "pos": [
        7525,
        7548
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "The worker nodes are not directly accessible from outside the Azure datacenter, but they can be accessed from the cluster head node via SSH.",
      "pos": [
        7550,
        7690
      ]
    },
