      ],
      "content": "If you use an SSH key to authenticate, in the <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Category<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> section, expand <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Connection<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, expand <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>SSH<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept>, and then select <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>Auth<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept>."
